Title: Desperate Doings in the Dungeon
Actors: Gorden Kaye, Guy Siner, Carmen Silvera
Plot: Herr Flick, dragged up as Irma von Kinkenrotten - the disguise he used to plant the bug - is still in the dungeon. Colonel von Strohm and General von Klinkerhoffen, aware that he knows of the forgeries, feel he should be silenced ...
